about.description:
Google Cloud Memorystore for Redis API is a Google Cloud service that lets client applications communicate with a fully managed Redis service for Google Cloud. Applications running on Google Cloud can achieve extreme performance by leveraging the highly scalable, available, secure Redis service without the burden of managing complex Redis deployments.
See the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/redis/latest/index.html#quick-start).
about.summary: Google Cloud Memorystore for Redis API client library

name: google-cloud-redis
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "google-cloud-redis" %}
{% set version = "2.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c783118462d9272fb9f519ef43b6ce383e99ad631e922a1f06fbef7148aec7b8

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - google-api-core-grpc >=1.22.2,<2.0.0dev
    - libcst >=0.2.5
    - proto-plus >=1.4.0
    - python >=3.6

test:
  imports:
    - grpc
    - google.cloud.redis
    - google.cloud.redis_v1
  commands:
    - pip check
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/googleapis/python-redis
  license: Apache-2.0
  license_family: Apache
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Google Cloud Memorystore for Redis API client library'
  description: Google Cloud Memorystore for Redis API is a Google Cloud service that lets client applications
    communicate with a fully managed Redis service for Google Cloud. Applications running on Google Cloud can
    achieve extreme performance by leveraging the highly scalable, available, secure Redis service without the
    burden of managing complex Redis deployments.

    See the [quick start guide](https://googleapis.dev/python/redis/latest/index.html#quick-start).

  doc_url: https://googleapis.dev/python/redis/latest/index.html
  dev_url: https://github.com/googleapis/python-redis

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - parthea
    - xylar
